001package com.technototes.library.hardware;
002
003public class FailedDevice implements com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.HardwareDevice {
004
005    protected String name;
006
007    protected FailedDevice(String deviceName) {
008        name = deviceName;
009    }
010
011    @Override
012    public Manufacturer getManufacturer() {
013        return Manufacturer.Other;
014    }
015
016    @Override
017    public String getDeviceName() {
018        return name;
019    }
020
021    @Override
022    public String getConnectionInfo() {
023        return "NC";
024    }
025
026    @Override
027    public int getVersion() {
028        return 0;
029    }
030
031    @Override
032    public void resetDeviceConfigurationForOpMode() {}
033
034    @Override
035    public void close() {}
036}
